      <title>沙特矿业公司 Maaden 认为沙特阿美燃油价格上涨影响盈利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/saudi-miner-maaden-says-aramco-fuel-price-hike-may-hit-earnings</link>
